  (text "SENSING: 2m shunt (Kelvin) between VOUT_INT and disconnect. INA240A3 (x100,\n0.2V/A, 1.6V @ 8A) feeds the CC loop; INA228 feeds telemetry. V divider /8 from\nVOUT terminals. NT1 = the single AGND-PGND tie point: at the shunt ground pad." (at 33.02 40.64 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid b8312d2d-da91-40ea-8369-78762059a1c5))
